{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Computes accessibility contrast ratio between two colors in hexadecimal strings."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If the hexadecimal strings are colors format in RGBA, will use their format in RGB (i.e. apply opacity, not truncate)."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/contrastRatios(_:_:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"contrastRatios","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"lhs","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"rhs","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OUDSFoundations15OUDSWCAG21RatioV","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"lhs","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"One color to test"}]}]},{"name":"rhs","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Another color to test"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"return-value","level":2,"text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The computed ratio and flags saying if it match 3:1, 4.5:1 or 7:1"}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See https:\/\/www.w3.org\/WAI\/WCAG21\/Techniques\/general\/G18.html#procedure"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Foundations"}],"externalID":"s:15OUDSFoundations15OUDSWCAG21RatioV14contrastRatiosyACSgSS_SStFZ","fragments":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"contrastRatios","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OUDSFoundations15OUDSWCAG21RatioV","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"contrastRatios(_:_:)","symbolKind":"method"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio\/contrastratios(_:_:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio"]]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"references":{"https://accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr":{"type":"link","url":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","title":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité"}]},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Some countries set up new laws so as to force companies to have a better accessibility of their digital services."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is for example the case for France with the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"also named “RGAA”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define whether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See for example "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","isActive":true}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio","role":"symbol","title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio"},"https://system.design.orange.com/0c1af118d/p/2531b9-accessibility-compliance":{"type":"link","url":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","title":"the following guidelines","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"the following guidelines"}]},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","title":"Founda